additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Not to be used for any purpose, or in any manner, contrary to this label unless authorised. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. May cause allergic reaction by skin contact. If product comes into contact with people, pets or plants, rinse thoroughly with water or mild soap solution. Treated surfaces may be slippery when wet. After use, wipe up excess product with a clean cloth or paper towel until surface is no longer slippery. To avoid staining surfaces, test product on a small inconspicuous area first.
